1.3.2 Manually
--------------

Check out the source code for dependencies and install them.  Then,
clone this repo to a directory of your choice, e.g.
‘~/.emacs.d/packages’.  Finally, add this to your config:
     (add-to-list 'load-path "~/.emacs.d/packages")
     (require 'org-gtd)


