1.4.4 Recommended key bindings
------------------------------

There’s an important keymap you’ll want to make the flow of processing
the inbox smoother.  I suggest ‘C-c c’.

     (define-key org-gtd-process-map (kbd "C-c c") #'org-gtd-choose)

